  ├── picod/                        # PicoD execution engine (files, execute, auth, server)\n│   ├── router/                       # Router (proxy, JWT, middleware, session_manager, loadbalancer)\n│   ├── store/                        # Redis/Valkey session store\n│   └── workloadmanager/              # Workload manager (handlers, reconciler, response)\n├── project.md                        # Project context document\n├── proposal.md                       # AR-028: SDK AgentRuntimeClient proposal\n├── python-sdk/                       # Python SDK (agentcube package + tests)\n├── sandbox-orchestration/            # Sandbox orchestration specs\n├── session-routing/                  # Session routing design/spec\n├── session-store/                    # Session store specs\n├── tasks.md                          # AR-023: CLI invoke/status tasks\n├── test/                             # Test scripts (makefile, chart render)\n├── test_spec.md                      # TDD specification (test cases for all components)\n└── testing/                          # Testing infrastructure\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Client-Go Related Code\n\nThe `client-go/` directory contains a **manually written** (not code-generated) Go client library with the following structure:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/clientset/clientset.go` | Defines `Interface` with `RuntimeV1alpha1()` method |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/clientset/real.go` | `Clientset` struct with `NewForConfig()` (stub - returns empty Clientset) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/clientset/fake.go` | `FakeClientset` with in-memory `ObjectStore` for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter - fully functional for testing |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/interfaces.go` | Defines `AgentRuntimeInterface`, `CodeInterpreterInterface`, `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` with standard K8s CRUD methods |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/client.go` | `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` factory, GVR definitions |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | **Core implementation**: `ObjectStore` (thread-safe in-memory store) + `AgentRuntimeClient` + `CodeInterpreterClient` with full CRUD (Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, Get, List, Watch, Patch) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/informers/externalversions/factory.go` | `SharedInformerFactory` interface and stub implementation |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | Runtime group interface |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | Informer interfaces with stub `cache.SharedIndexInformer` implementations |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | Fully implemented `AgentRuntimeLister` and `CodeInterpreterLister` with namespace-scoped listers |\n\n**Key observation**: The client-go is manually written, not generated by `code-generator` tools. There is no `hack/` directory with code generation scripts. The real clientset (`real.go`) is a stub - `NewForConfig` returns an empty `Clientset{}`. Only the fake client is fully functional.\n\n---\n\n### 3. API Definitions for runtime/v1alpha1\n\n**API Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n\n#### AgentRuntime Type\nLocation: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ObjectMeta\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort       `json:\"targetPort,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate   `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration   `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration   `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels      map[string]string\n    Annotations map[string]string\n    Spec        corev1.PodSpec   // Full K8s PodSpec\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ListMeta\n    Items []AgentRuntime\n}\n```\n\nKubebuilder markers: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes`, printcolumn for Age.\n\n#### CodeInterpreter Type\nLocation: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ObjectMeta\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort                     `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate  `json:\"template\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration                 `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration                 `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32                           `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType                     `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels           map[string]string\n    Annotations      map[string]string\n    RuntimeClassName *string\n    Image            string\n    ImagePullPolicy  corev1.PullPolicy\n    ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference\n    Environment      []corev1.EnvVar\n    Command          []string\n    Args             []string\n    Resources        corev1.ResourceRequirements\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n    Ready      bool\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ListMeta\n    Items []CodeInterpreter\n}\n```\n\nKubebuilder markers: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=codeinterpreters`, printcolumn for Age.\n\n#### Shared Types\nLocation: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string    // \"HTTP\", \"HTTPS\"\ntype AuthModeType string    // \"picod\", \"none\"\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string\n    Name       string\n    Port       uint32\n    Protocol   ProtocolType\n}\n```\n\n#### Constants\nLocation: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go`\n\n```go\nAnnotationKeyRuntime = \"agentcube.io/runtime\"\nAnnotationKeyVersion = \"agentcube.io/version\"\n```\n\n#### GroupVersion Info\nLocation: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n\n```go\nGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\nSchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\nAddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\nSchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion  // alias\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Code Generation Setup\n\n**There is NO code generation infrastructure in this project.** Specifically:\n\n- **No `hack/` directory** exists\n- **No `code-generator`** tooling (no `update-codegen.sh`, `boilerplate.go.txt`, etc.)\n- **No `controller-gen`** Makefile targets\n- The `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` files exist but appear to be manually maintained or generated externally\n- The `client-go/` library is entirely **hand-written**, not generated by `client-gen`, `lister-gen`, or `informer-gen`\n- The Makefile has no `generate`, `codegen`, or `manifests` targets\n\nThe Makefile (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile`) provides:\n- `build` - Compiles 4 Go binaries: `router`, `workloadmanager`, `agentd`, `picod`\n- `test` / `test-coverage` - `go test ./...`\n- `lint` / `fmt` / `vet` - Code quality\n- `docker` - Builds Docker images\n- `helm-lint` / `helm-template` - Helm chart validation\n- `python-lint` / `python-test` - Python SDK quality\n\n---\n\n### 5. Design Documents and Architecture Docs\n\n| Document | Location | Purpose |\n|----------|----------|---------|\n| **project.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` | Project context: K8s-native sandbox orchestration platform, tech stack, architecture diagram, conventions |\n| **design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` | AR-029: Python SDK HTTP client design (792 lines) - architecture, data structures, API contracts, testing strategy |\n| **proposal.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` | AR-028: SDK AgentRuntimeClient proposal - scope, impact analysis, alternatives, implementation notes |\n| **delta-spec.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` | AR-029: Detailed Gherkin-style scenarios for HTTP client behavior |\n| **test_spec.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` | TDD specification with test cases for WM, Router, Store, PicoD, SDK |\n| **tasks.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` | AR-023: CLI invoke/status command tasks with dependency graph |\n| **integrations/spec.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/spec.md` | Dify plugin + PCAP analyzer integration requirements |\n| **changes/AR-031/design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md` | RBAC configuration design (689 lines) - Helm chart RBAC refactoring |\n| **changes/AR-030/** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/` | Helm chart templates and values |\n| **changes/AR-015/** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/` | Earlier change request |\n| **changes/AR-014/** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-014/` | Earlier change request |\n| **changes/AR-003/** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/` | Earlier change request |\n| **code-execution/design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/code-execution/design.md` | Code execution design |\n| **session-routing/design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md` | Session routing design |\n| **idle-cleanup/design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md` | Idle cleanup design |\n| **ci-cd/design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md` | CI/CD design |\n| **python-sdk/design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/design.md` | Python SDK design |\n\n---\n\n### 6. pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 Directory Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── agent_type.go              # AgentRuntime, AgentRuntimeSpec, SandboxTemplate, AgentRuntimeStatus, AgentRuntimeList\n├── agent_type_test.go         # 235 lines - DeepCopy tests, default values, all-fields tests\n├── codeinterpreter_types.go   # CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterList\n├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go  # 654 lines - Comprehensive DeepCopy, defaults, all-fields, nil-field tests\n├── shared_types.go            # ProtocolType, AuthModeType, TargetPort\n├── shared_types_test.go       # 77 lines - Constant and TargetPort tests\n├── constants.go               # AnnotationKeyRuntime, AnnotationKeyVersion\n├── constants_test.go          # 21 lines - Constant verification tests\n├── groupversion_info.go       # GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme, Kind constants, Resource() helper\n├── groupversion_info_test.go  # 80 lines - Scheme registration, GVK/GVR tests\n├── doc.go                     # // +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package, // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n└── zz_generated.deepcopy.go   # 324 lines - DeepCopyInto/DeepCopy/DeepCopyObject for all types\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. Testing Infrastructure\n\n#### Go Tests (28 test files total)\n\n**API tests** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`):\n- `agent_type_test.go` - AgentRuntime deepcopy, defaults, all-fields\n- `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` - CodeInterpreter deepcopy, defaults, all-fields, nil handling\n- `shared_types_test.go` - ProtocolType/AuthModeType constants, TargetPort\n- `constants_test.go` - Annotation key constants\n- `groupversion_info_test.go` - Scheme registration, GVK/GVR validation\n\n**Component tests**:\n- `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` - Idle cleanup reconciler\n- `pkg/picod/` - server_test.go, execute_test.go, auth_test.go, health_test.go, config_test.go, sanitize_test.go, files/*_test.go\n- `pkg/router/` - server_test.go, middleware_test.go, jwt_test.go, config_test.go\n- `pkg/store/` - store_redis_test.go, store_valkey_test.go, singleton_test.go, codec_test.go\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/` - sandbox_lifecycle_test.go, sandbox_delete_test.go, response_test.go, metrics_test.go\n\n#### Python Tests\n\n**Python SDK** (`python-sdk/tests/`):\n- `test_agent_runtime.py`, `test_code_interpreter.py`, `test_control_plane.py`, `test_data_plane.py`, `test_exceptions.py`, `test_imports.py`, `test_utils.py`\n\n**CLI** (`cmd/cli/tests/`):\n- `cli/test_build_command.py`, `cli/test_invoke_command.py`, `cli/test_status_command.py`\n- `runtime/test_build_runtime_*.py`, `runtime/test_invoke_runtime.py`, `runtime/test_status_runtime.py`, `runtime/test_publish_runtime.py`, `runtime/test_pack_runtime_*.py`\n- `services/test_agentcube_provider.py`, `services/test_k8s_provider.py`, `services/test_metadata_service.py`, `services/test_metadata_model.py`, `services/test_docker_service.py`\n- `models/test_pack_models.py`\n- `integration/test_build_e2e.py`\n\n---\n\n### 8. Design Patterns and Conventions\n\n1. **Change Request (AR) Workflow**: Each feature follows an AR (AgentCube Request) number with standardized documents: `proposal.md`, `design.md`, `delta-spec.md`, `tasks.md`\n\n2. **Go package layout**: `pkg/` for libraries, `cmd/` for binaries, following standard Go project conventions\n\n3. **Kubernetes API conventions**:\n   - Uses `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` markers\n   - `GroupVersion` pattern with `SchemeBuilder` from `controller-runtime`\n   - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` for DeepCopy methods\n   - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` and `+groupName`\n\n4. **Client-go pattern**: Standard K8s client-go structure (clientset, informers, listers) but **manually implemented** rather than code-generated. Uses an in-memory `ObjectStore` pattern for the fake client.\n\n5. **Python SDK architecture**: Facade pattern - high-level clients (`CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient`) delegate to internal data plane/control plane clients\n\n6. **Testing**: Uses `testify/assert` for Go, `pytest` for Python. DeepCopy isolation tests verify that modifications to copies do not affect originals.\n\n7. **Helm chart**: Standard Helm 3 chart with CRDs, RBAC separation, values-driven conditional rendering\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2854859a2ffe5cTQrqGU5T6isi","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775880349274,"end":1775880556925}}}}
