{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880566149,"sessionID":"ses_285489331ffe7fl4FcwAl9BTUV","part":{"id":"prt_d7abaf121001dB9oAdj637TkHu","messageID":"msg_d7abad1da001Ac39CPIBsxL1Td","sessionID":"ses_285489331ffe7fl4FcwAl9BTUV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_e4b62790504b490c9809ae0e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) — Design/设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n6: \n7: 本变更统一并规范化 AgentCube Helm chart 中的 RBAC 资源配置。当前 RBAC 定义分散在多个模板文件中（`rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`、`rbac-router.yaml`、`volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml`），命名风格不一致，且 Volcano 调度器的 RBAC 与非 RBAC 资源混杂在同一模板中。\n8: \n9: 本变更将所有 RBAC 资源收敛至 `templates/rbac/` 目录，统一通过 `values.yaml` 控制开关，确保所有 ServiceAccount/Role(ClusterRole)/RoleBinding(ClusterRoleBinding) 遵循一致的命名规范和标签约定。这是 RBAC 配置的基础设施重构，不改变任何权限范围。\n10: \n11: ### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\n12: \n13: **当前状态 (Before):**\n14: \n15: ```\n16: manifests/charts/base/templates/\n17: ├── workloadmanager.yaml                  # WM Deployment + Service\n18: ├── agentcube-router.yaml                 # Router Deployment + Service\n19: ├── rbac/\n20: │   └── workloadmanager.yaml              # WM SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (无 values gate)\n21: ├── rbac-router.yaml                      # Router SA + Role + RoleBinding (条件渲染)\n22: └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment (混合)\n23: ```\n24: \n25: **目标状态 (After):**\n26: \n27: ```\n28: manifests/charts/base/templates/\n29: ├── workloadmanager.yaml                  # WM Deployment + Service (不变)\n30: ├── agentcube-router.yaml                 # Router Deployment + Service (不变)\n31: ├── rbac/\n32: │   ├── workloadmanager.yaml              # WM SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (添加 values gate + 重命名)\n33: │   ├── router.yaml                       # Router SA + Role + RoleBinding (从 rbac-router.yaml 迁入)\n34: │   └── volcano-scheduler.yaml            # SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (从 volcano 模板抽取)\n35: └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # 仅保留 ConfigMap + Service + Deployment\n36: ```\n37: \n38: ### 1.3 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n39: \n40: ```\n41: AR-031 RBAC 配置\n42:   ├── 前置依赖\n43:   │   ├── AR-030 (Helm Chart 模板与 Values)     # 基线 chart 结构\n44:   │   ├── Kubernetes RBAC API v1                # rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n45:   │   └── Helm 3                                # 资源追踪和生命周期管理\n46:   │\n47:   ├── 模板渲染依赖\n48:   │   ├── _helpers.tpl                          # agentcube.rbacName, agentcube.rbacBindingName\n49:   │   └── values.yaml                           # workloadmanager.rbac.create, router.rbac.create, volcano.scheduler.rbac.create\n50:   │\n51:   └── 验证工具\n52:       ├── helm lint                             # 模板语法和结构验证\n53:       ├── helm template                         # 渲染结果验证\n54:       └── kubectl apply --dry-run=client        # Kubernetes 资源有效性验证\n55: ```\n56: \n57: ### 1.4 RBAC 资源矩阵 (RBAC Resource Matrix)\n58: \n59: | 组件 | ServiceAccount | Role 类型 | Role 名称 | 绑定类型 | 绑定名称 | 条件开关 | 默认值 |\n60: |------|---------------|-----------|-----------|---------|---------|---------|--------|\n61: | WorkloadManager | `workloadmanager` | ClusterRole | `agentcube-workloadmanager` | ClusterRoleBinding | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | `workloadmanager.rbac.create` | `true` |\n62: | Router | `agentcube-router` (或自定义) | Role (namespace) | `agentcube-router` | RoleBinding | `agentcube-router-binding` | `router.rbac.create` | `false` |\n63: | Volcano Scheduler | `volcano-agent-scheduler` | ClusterRole | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler` | ClusterRoleBinding | `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding` | `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` | 跟随 `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n64: \n65: ### 1.5 命名规范 (Naming Convention)\n66: \n67: | 资源类型 | 命名规则 | 示例 | 说明 |\n68: |----------|---------|------|------|\n69: | ServiceAccount | `<component>` 或 `agentcube-<component>` | `workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router` | 与 Deployment 命名保持一致，不添加额外前缀 |\n70: | ClusterRole/Role | `agentcube-<component>` | `agentcube-workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router` | 添加 `agentcube-` 前缀避免集群级命名冲突 |\n71: | ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding | `agentcube-<component>-binding` | `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding` | 添加 `agentcube-` 前缀和 `-binding` 后缀 |\n72: \n73: 名称长度限制：Kubernetes 资源名称最大 63 字符。`_helpers.tpl` 中的 helper 函数 SHALL 对超长名称进行 `trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\"` 处理。\n74: \n75: ---\n76: \n77: ## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n78: \n79: ### 2.1 values.yaml RBAC 键树\n80: \n81: ```yaml\n82: workloadmanager:\n83:   rbac:\n84:     create: true                    # 新增: 控制 WM RBAC 资源渲染, 默认 true 保持向后兼容\n85: \n86: router:\n87:   rbac:\n88:     create: false                   # 已存在: 控制 Router RBAC 资源渲染, 默认 false\n89:   serviceAccountName: \"\"            # 已存在: 自定义 SA 名称 (影响 Router RBAC 资源命名)\n90: \n91: volcano:\n92:   scheduler:\n93:     enabled: false                  # 已存在: 控制 Volcano 调度器整体渲染\n94:     rbac:\n95:       create: \"\"                    # 新增: 空字符串表示跟随 enabled; 显式 true/false 覆盖\n96: ```\n97: \n98: ### 2.2 values.yaml 键树关系图 (RBAC 部分)\n99: \n100: ```\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 689. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) — Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n\n本变更统一并规范化 AgentCube Helm chart 中的 RBAC 资源配置。当前 RBAC 定义分散在多个模板文件中（`rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`、`rbac-router.yaml`、`volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml`），命名风格不一致，且 Volcano 调度器的 RBAC 与非 RBAC 资源混杂在同一模板中。\n\n本变更将所有 RBAC 资源收敛至 `templates/rbac/` 目录，统一通过 `values.yaml` 控制开关，确保所有 ServiceAccount/Role(ClusterRole)/RoleBinding(ClusterRoleBinding) 遵循一致的命名规范和标签约定。这是 RBAC 配置的基础设施重构，不改变任何权限范围。\n\n### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\n\n**当前状态 (Before):**\n\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/\n├── workloadmanager.yaml                  # WM Deployment + Service\n├── agentcube-router.yaml                 # Router Deployment + Service\n├── rbac/\n│   └── workloadmanager.yaml              # WM SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (无 values gate)","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md","time":{"start":1775880566137,"end":1775880566147}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880567262,"sessionID":"ses_285489331ffe7fl4FcwAl9BTUV","part":{"id":"prt_d7abaf5ea001LnJmmG0F2lS8Lj","messageID":"msg_d7abad1da001Ac39CPIBsxL1Td","sessionID":"ses_285489331ffe7fl4FcwAl9BTUV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7107ba8ae5bc4eef9f01ed53","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-029: SDK HTTP 底层客户端 — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: This AR covers the HTTP底层客户端 (HTTP underlying client layer) for the AgentCube Python SDK. It provides:\n8: \n9: 1. **Control Plane Client** — HTTP client for Workload Manager session lifecycle (create/delete sessions).\n10: 2. **Code Interpreter Data Plane Client** — HTTP client for Router-based code execution and file operations.\n11: 3. **Agent Runtime Data Plane Client** — HTTP client for Router-based agent invocation.\n12: 4. **HTTP Utilities** — Session factory, token reader, logger factory.\n13: 5. **Exception Hierarchy** — Structured error types for SDK operations.\n14: \n15: ### 1.2 System Context\n16: \n17: ```\n18: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n19: │                         User Application                            │\n20: │  ┌───────────────────────────┐   ┌─────────────────────────────┐   │\n21: │  │   CodeInterpreterClient   │   │    AgentRuntimeClient       │   │\n22: │  │   (High-level facade)     │   │    (High-level facade)      │   │\n23: │  └───────────┬───────────────┘   └──────────────┬──────────────┘   │\n24: │              │                                   │                   │\n25: │  ┌───────────▼───────────────┐   ┌──────────────▼──────────────┐   │\n26: │  │   ControlPlaneClient      │   │   CodeInterpreterDataPlane  │   │\n27: │  │   (Workload Manager)      │   │   AgentRuntimeDataPlane     │   │\n28: │  └───────────┬───────────────┘   └──────────────┬──────────────┘   │\n29: └──────────────┼──────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────┘\n30:                │                                  │\n31:                ▼                                  ▼\n32:     ┌──────────────────────┐          ┌────────────────────────┐\n33:     │  Workload Manager    │          │  Router (Data Plane)   │\n34:     │  (Control Plane API) │          │  /v1/namespaces/...    │\n35:     └──────────────────────┘          └────────────────────────┘\n36: ```\n37: \n38: ### 1.3 Design Principles\n39: \n40: - **No single `Configuration` class**: Defaults and environment resolution are distributed across client constructors.\n41: - **Context manager support**: All clients support `with` statement for proper resource cleanup.\n42: - **Session header convention**: Lowercase `x-agentcube-session-id` for all Router requests.\n43: - **Timeout safety**: Read timeout buffer (`+2.0s`) for command execution to avoid premature `ReadTimeout`.\n44: - **Connection pooling**: `HTTPAdapter` with configurable pool size for all HTTP sessions.\n45: \n46: ### 1.4 Package Structure\n47: \n48: ```\n49: sdk-python/\n50: ├── pyproject.toml                          # Package metadata, dependencies\n51: ├── agentcube/\n52: │   ├── __init__.py                         # Public exports: CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient\n53: │   ├── code_interpreter.py                 # CodeInterpreterClient (high-level facade)\n54: │   ├── agent_runtime.py                    # AgentRuntimeClient (high-level facade)\n55: │   ├── exceptions.py                       # Exception hierarchy\n56: │   ├── clients/\n57: │   │   ├── __init__.py                     # Re-exports: ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient, AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n58: │   │   ├── control_plane.py                # ControlPlaneClient (Workload Manager HTTP)\n59: │   │   ├── code_interpreter_data_plane.py  # CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient (Router HTTP)\n60: │   │   └── agent_runtime_data_plane.py     # AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient (Router HTTP)\n61: │   └── utils/\n62: │       ├── __init__.py                     # Empty module marker\n63: │       ├── http.py                         # create_session()\n64: │       ├── utils.py                        # read_token_from_file()\n65: │       └── log.py                          # get_logger()\n66: ├── examples/\n67: │   ├── basic_usage.py\n68: │   └── agent_runtime_usage.py\n69: ├── scripts/\n70: │   └── e2e_picod_test.py\n71: └── tests/\n72:     ├── test_code_interpreter.py\n73:     ├── test_agent_runtime.py\n74:     ├── test_control_plane.py\n75:     ├── test_data_plane.py\n76:     └── test_exceptions.py\n77: ```\n78: \n79: ### 1.5 Dependencies\n80: \n81: ```toml\n82: dependencies = [\n83:     \"requests\",\n84:     \"PyJWT>=2.0.0\",\n85:     \"cryptography\",\n86: ]\n87: \n88: requires-python = \">=3.10\"\n89: \n90: [build-system]\n91: requires = [\"setuptools>=61.0\", \"wheel\"]\n92: build-backend = \"setuptools.build_meta\"\n93: \n94: [tool.setuptools.packages.find]\n95: where = [\".\"]\n96: include = [\"agentcube*\"]\n97: namespaces = false\n98: ```\n99: \n100: ---\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 792. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-029: SDK HTTP 底层客户端 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\nThis AR covers the HTTP底层客户端 (HTTP underlying client layer) for the AgentCube Python SDK. It provides:\n\n1. **Control Plane Client** — HTTP client for Workload Manager session lifecycle (create/delete sessions).\n2. **Code Interpreter Data Plane Client** — HTTP client for Router-based code execution and file operations.\n3. **Agent Runtime Data Plane Client** — HTTP client for Router-based agent invocation.\n4. **HTTP Utilities** — Session factory, token reader, logger factory.\n5. **Exception Hierarchy** — Structured error types for SDK operations.\n\n### 1.2 System Context\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         User Application                            │\n│  ┌───────────────────────────┐   ┌─────────────────────────────┐   │","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775880567253,"end":1775880567261}}}}
